It's a pain just reading it.

64
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:22,220
Now, now, don't say that.

65
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:27,980
It's important for Salamanders to learn
the workings of Aqua, Akatsuki.

66
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:31,880
I know that!

67
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:36,900
This doesn't look like a study session...
It's more like Al's just tutoring you.

68
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:39,130
What did you say, Gachapen?!

69
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:41,400
Don't call me Gachapen, Pony-boy!

70
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,800
I'll go buy us some coffee.

71
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:45,900
