72
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,340
Get another cup for us, too.

73
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:48,610
Okay...
Get another cup for us, too.

74
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:50,010
Okay...

75
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,850
Well then, study hard!

76
00:05:53,850 --> 00:05:54,480
Will do.

77
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:54,820
Take care.
Will do.

78
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:55,940
Take care.

79
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,520
Promotion exam, huh?

80
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:03,390
You two will probably have yours soon, too.

81
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:05,160
