this shop is really delicious.

91
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:39,590
Oh?

92
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:42,830
You're right! They look delicious!

93
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,230
My, my.
You're right! They look delicious!

94
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:44,030
My, my.

95
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:48,200
Let's eat!
Let's eat!

96
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:53,640
The salmon is delicious!

97
00:06:57,110 --> 00:07:01,640
We don't have any bookings for this afternoon,
so maybe we can call it a day.

98
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:07,590
