so it feels a little lonely, doesn't it?

99
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:12,260
Oh, no! President Aria!

100
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:14,490
Oh, my! Water, water!

101
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:16,730
Here's a glass of water, Akari.

102
00:07:16,730 --> 00:07:17,600
Okay.

103
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,620
Here, President Aria.

104
00:07:22,770 --> 00:07:24,840
Looks like he'll be okay.

105
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:27,900
