118
00:07:59,470 --> 00:08:01,270
Thank you very much!

119
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:03,710
Well then, see you later.

120
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:04,540
Yes!

121
00:08:06,850 --> 00:08:09,420
It's addressed to you, Alicia.

122
00:08:09,420 --> 00:08:11,910
My, my. I wonder what it is?

123
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:18,090
"Bringing you spring a little early."

124
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:21,550
My, it's from a customer
we had during Carnevale.

125
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:24,500
