who came with her daughter.

126
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:26,400
Ah, I remember.

127
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:29,460
They were from the south, right?

128
00:08:29,570 --> 00:08:33,230
It's cherry tea and cherry jam.

129
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:38,200
