invite everyone over?

130
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:40,510
What a great idea!

131
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:44,850
It's slow this time of year, so Akira
and Athena might be able to join us, too.

132
00:08:44,850 --> 00:08:46,880
I'll try calling them.

133
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:49,050
My, my.

134
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,400
Seeing Neo-Venezia after Carnevale...

135
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:06,740
