My hand?

205
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:46,210
Like this?

206
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:20,650
Oh, my!

207
00:14:20,890 --> 00:14:22,380
Snow!

208
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:27,860
It's snowing!

209
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,630
It's beautiful.

210
00:14:29,730 --> 00:14:32,460
Yes, it sure is.

211
00:14:33,130 --> 00:14:36,690
What a wonderful gift!

212
00:14:38,810 --> 00:14:45,470
The cold snow brought warmth to our
customers' hearts, as well as our own.

213
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,180
Yes.

214
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:48,850
No sa... pp... y...

215
00:14:48,850 --> 00:14:51,090
You're too amazing, Alicia.

216
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,550
My, my.

217
00:14:52,890 --> 00:14:56,220
Alicia's amazing, but so is Akira.

218
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:58,790
Huh? Did something happen?

219
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:04,030
How do I look? It suits me, right?

220
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,130
