221
00:15:05,130 --> 00:15:05,730
Hey, cut it out!

222
00:15:05,730 --> 00:15:06,890
It's not safe!

223
00:15:06,970 --> 00:15:11,840
It's fine, it's fine!
I have good sense of balance!

224
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:15,780
