No! No! Buy me ice cream! Ice cream!

248
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,370
No, no, no, no!

249
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,910
What's with him all of a sudden?

250
00:17:04,950 --> 00:17:10,160
Even though Athena looked
pretty dopey, it was really cool.

